summary:
I don’t think a lot of people realise but Namjoon has grown so beautifully over the years, it’s surreal.
I’ve never seen someone...
body:
Honestly though,

I don’t think a lot of people realise but Namjoon has grown so beautifully over the years, it’s surreal.

I’ve never seen someone who has accepted all his past, all the things, good or bad so gracefully. The very fact that he doesn’t try to cover his past and his so called flaws but takes them into his stride by turning them into lyrics that thousands will sing right back to him.

The very fact that Kim Namjoon had the audacity to address the ‘but Namjoon’ fiasco and in such a way that no joke, the haters are quaking. You cannot use his past as a weapon again him cause he has full well acknowledged and accepted it. You loose.

Basically, you’re ding dong, he’s ddaeng.

NOTHING but respect for my president. 👑
